                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "50c9dd58-df68-4ae2-9888-1b6ec6df02f1",
            "content": "A good password is a password that is: At least 14 char long  has characters of all the following categories: Uppercase characters Lowercase characters Digits Special characters like #@<*&(^%$>![space]. Is not used for another account Was used in the last year not compromised not easy to guess not common  not in a dictionary as random as possible (generated by a password manager)",
            "tags": [
                {
                    "id": "Password",
                    "text": "Password"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "18d799a1-c138-4d3b-99c6-663fa7176f49",
            "content": "Acceptable second factors are: TOTP Apps such as Google Authenticator, Bitwarden Authenticator A Physical Security Token YubiKey from Yubico SMS only as a backup 2nd Factor.",
